snippet.title: First Look: Farcana Gameplay
snippet.description:
Farcana is a team-arena PvP shooter built by industry leaders. 

We’re thrilled to announce our official Alpha version, where you can see long-awaited gameplay with 4 characters, mechanics, and the first arena with 2 zones to conquer!

Our Alpha Tournament will take place soon, so watch this space for more information on taking part in the fight for Bitcoin on Mars.

Learn more on our socials 

Discord: https://discord.gg/Farcana
Website: https://www.farcana.com
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/farcanaofficial
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/farcana_official
Medium: https://farcana.medium.com/
Telegram: https://t.me/FarcanaGame
